FBIS3-18081 "drweu039aa_94015" FBIS-WEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Western Leaders Comment on Hebron Mosque Massacre Swiss Ministry Condemns Attack LD2502160594 LD2502160594 Article Type:BFN [Editorial Report] Bern Swiss Radio International in English at 1500 GMT on 25 February carries a 2-minute report on the Hebron mosque massacre today. The announcer says: "Meanwhile, countries throughout the world, including Switzerland, have condemned the Hebron massacre. The Swiss Foreign Ministry in Bern said Switzerland hoped that Israel and the PLO would continue their peace negotiations."
